<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h2>Welcome to the Student Performance Tracking and Prediction Tool</h2>

    <p>
        This tool is designed for personal use to track your study sessions and breaks,
        and generate reports based on your study patterns. It provides insights into your
        academic progress and can help predict your future grades.
    </p>

    <h3>Features:</h3>

    <ul>
        <li>
            Record and manage your study sessions, including start time, end time, duration, subject, and notes.
        </li>
        <li>
            Track breaks taken during study sessions, specifying start time, end time, duration, and description.
        </li>
        <li>
            View a weekly schedule showing study sessions and breaks for each day.
        </li>
        <li>
            Analyze your study patterns to understand your productivity and optimize your learning schedule.
        </li>
        <li>
            Predict your academic status and potential grades based on your study habits and historical data.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Usage:</h3>

    <p>
        Start by adding your current knowledge on the subject matter and then record your study progress and breaks
        for each day. You can add one-off sessions or recurring ones to build a comprehensive view of your study routine.
    </p>

    <h3>Get Started:</h3>

    <p>
        To begin using the tool, navigate to the respective sections for adding study sessions and breaks, or view
        the weekly schedule to see your planned study sessions and breaks.
    </p>
</div>
